em-HrC2kT8Vpvjd5nkCL9ieng">Nguyễn lang quy - Nguyệt hạ cảm sự - 阮郎歸－月下感事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t-T%E1%BB%95/author-wLBO_S7oDu5BwDnRbL0Axg">Sử Đạt Tổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%B7c-ti%E1%BA%BFn-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-s8pvx0df95gLN0RH5t-XnA">Tặng đặc tiến Nhữ Dương vương nhị thập vận - 贈特進汝陽王二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/T%C3%A2n-di-%E1%BB%95/poem-eT5D6E1r09NoW4TOq3c4fA">Tân di ổ - 辛夷塢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Thu hứng kỳ 6 - 秋興其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%E1%BB%95-t%E1%BB%B1-hoa/poem-yp9Sm_s4lIfDiKEc2e0h7g">Vịnh cổ tự hoa - 詠古寺花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-mmPw1MZmtgbKEg6cv2Vw1A">Tư Không Thự</a>)<br></div>	</div>
